ğŸŸ© 1ï¸âƒ£ VPC (Virtual Private Cloud)
âœ” Why do we need it?

A VPC is your private isolated network inside AWS.

Think of it like:

Your own private data center inside AWS.

Inside the VPC you place:

EC2

RDS

Load Balancers

